<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 14:06:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哥伦比亚大学教师声明将哈马斯屠杀称为“军事行动”引起愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/columbia-faculty-statement-terming-hamas-massacre-military-action-draws-fury/0000018b-80ae-d4a8-a3cf-bcaf65880000</link><description>这封由哥伦比亚大学约 130 名教职员工签署的公开信表达了“对我们的一些学生如何成为人肉搜索、公开羞辱[和]监视的恶意目标的担忧”，并补充道，“做出此类主张……不能被视为反犹太主义” &amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 13:48:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/columbia-faculty-statement-terming-hamas-massacre-military-action-draws-fury/0000018b-80ae-d4a8-a3cf-bcaf65880000</guid></item><item><title>在最困难的时刻，以色列正由一个傀儡领导</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/in-its-most-difficult-hour-israel-is-being-led-by-a-puppet/0000018b-7fff-d4a8-a3cf-ffffaf3d0000</link><description>当以色列士兵在前线冒着生命危险，成千上万的公民生活在噩梦中时，内塔尼亚胡却在 X 上吐出污言秽语。 人们可以合理地假设 Bibi-Yair-Sara 轴心导致了诽谤。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 13:26:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/in-its-most-difficult-hour-israel-is-being-led-by-a-puppet/0000018b-7fff-d4a8-a3cf-ffffaf3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵因涉嫌射杀巴勒斯坦橄榄收割机而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-arrested-on-suspicion-of-fatally-shooting-palestinian-olive-harvester/0000018b-808c-d4ba-a3ab-9a8da2960000</link><description>枪击事件发生时，这名士兵正在以色列国防军正统派营休假，他说，他在以色列人和巴勒斯坦人发生冲突后鸣枪示警，这与当地巴勒斯坦人对事件的说法相矛盾</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 13:04:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-arrested-on-suspicion-of-fatally-shooting-palestinian-olive-harvester/0000018b-808c-d4ba-a3ab-9a8da2960000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔手上沾满了以色列的鲜血。这不是人质的诚实经纪人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/qatar-has-israeli-blood-on-its-hands-its-no-honest-broker-for-the-hostages/0000018b-803f-d4ba-a3ab-9abfa24f0000</link><description>卡塔尔资助了包括哈马斯在内的极端伊斯兰运动，并利用恐惧、羞耻和愤怒的情绪煽动叛乱，使与穆斯林兄弟会有联系的政治集团受益</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 12:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/qatar-has-israeli-blood-on-its-hands-its-no-honest-broker-for-the-hostages/0000018b-803f-d4ba-a3ab-9abfa24f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击杰宁难民营，四名巴勒斯坦枪手被打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/four-palestinian-gunmen-killed-in-israeli-army-raid-on-jenin-refugee-camp/0000018b-8060-d4ba-a3ab-9aedea7e0000</link><description>据以色列军队称，部队突袭了营地，发现了隐藏在道路下的爆炸物，并摧毁了一个装有诱杀装置的监视室</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 12:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/four-palestinian-gunmen-killed-in-israeli-army-raid-on-jenin-refugee-camp/0000018b-8060-d4ba-a3ab-9aedea7e0000</guid></item><item><title>他们逃离哈马斯到达地球最低的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-killed-their-neighbors-they-fled-to-the-lowest-place-on-earth/0000018b-6c37-db57-a7cb-ecbfe2ad0000</link><description>死海上的一家酒店已成为哈马斯贝埃里基布兹大屠杀幸存者的临时住所。他们不等政府就开始重建，他们对此感到愤怒</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 12:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-killed-their-neighbors-they-fled-to-the-lowest-place-on-earth/0000018b-6c37-db57-a7cb-ecbfe2ad0000</guid></item><item><title>在与哈马斯的战争最激烈的时候，内塔尼亚胡向以色列宣战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/at-the-height-of-war-with-hamas-netanyahu-declared-war-on-israel/0000018b-8007-d4a8-a3cf-bcaf6ac00000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡没有进行反省，而是将 10 月 7 日灾难的责任归咎于国防部长。 “如果他垮台，国家就会垮台，”首相的一位助手声称。但当群众从防空洞出来并要求内塔尼亚胡下台时，他的评价将再次崩溃</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 11:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/at-the-height-of-war-with-hamas-netanyahu-declared-war-on-israel/0000018b-8007-d4a8-a3cf-bcaf6ac00000</guid></item><item><title>威胁、暴力和种族主义言论：以色列对阿拉伯工人的敌意激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/threats-violence-and-racist-remarks-israel-sees-surge-of-hostility-against-arab-workers/0000018b-6c07-d326-a39b-6e1f9be30000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，许多阿拉伯公交车司机因对他们的敌意而停止上班 ■ 贝特谢梅什一家超市外的示威者要求解雇所有阿拉伯员工</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 11:45:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/threats-violence-and-racist-remarks-israel-sees-surge-of-hostility-against-arab-workers/0000018b-6c07-d326-a39b-6e1f9be30000</guid></item><item><title>“在加沙周围遭受酷刑和游行：”被绑架的以色列-德国狂欢者确认死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/tortured-and-paraded-around-gaza-abducted-israeli-german-raver-confirmed-dead/0000018b-8001-d1da-a1bb-edb9c2330000</link><description>两周前，德国媒体报道称，拥有德国和以色列双重国籍的 23 岁沙尼·洛克 (Shani Louk) 在加沙地带北部的一家医院病重，随后被证实死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 10:39:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/tortured-and-paraded-around-gaza-abducted-israeli-german-raver-confirmed-dead/0000018b-8001-d1da-a1bb-edb9c2330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报部建议哈马斯战争后将加沙人迁往西奈半岛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-document-suggests-possible-relocation-of-gazans-to-northern-sinai/0000018b-7ff6-d1da-a1bb-7ffe83ed0000</link><description>以色列情报部准备的一份文件草案提出了一种选择，即首先将加沙人口迁移到西奈半岛北部的帐篷城。这是政治领导层可能采取退出战争战略的第一个迹象</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 10:19:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-document-suggests-possible-relocation-of-gazans-to-northern-sinai/0000018b-7ff6-d1da-a1bb-7ffe83ed0000</guid></item><item><title>反犹太骚乱后警方控制俄罗斯达吉斯坦机场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/police-take-control-of-russias-dagestan-airport-after-antisemitic-riot/0000018b-7f8e-d51e-a3cb-7feeecb60000</link><description>该地区的骚乱令渴望维持国内稳定的俄罗斯总统普京头疼不已。达吉斯坦领导人谢尔盖·梅利科夫表示，这一事件严重违反了法律，尽管达吉斯坦人强调巴勒斯坦受害者的“痛苦”</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 09:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/police-take-control-of-russias-dagestan-airport-after-antisemitic-riot/0000018b-7f8e-d51e-a3cb-7feeecb60000</guid></item><item><title>包括美国在内的以色列各条战线的紧张局势都在酝酿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/in-the-south-north-and-with-the-u-s-israel-faces-an-escalation-on-all-fronts/0000018b-7d2e-d4a8-a3cf-fdaf26c90000</link><description>随着以色列在加沙的行动在保密的情况下扩大，政府希望增加的军事压力将推动被绑架者的谈判。 ■ 在约旦河西岸，定居者的暴力活动猖獗。以色列公众对内塔尼亚胡没有信心</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 05:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/in-the-south-north-and-with-the-u-s-israel-faces-an-escalation-on-all-fronts/0000018b-7d2e-d4a8-a3cf-fdaf26c90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的推文被党内同事视为“精神病”，可能会加速他的下台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tweet-could-hasten-his-ouster-party-colleagues-say/0000018b-7c8b-d51e-a3cb-7def36cb0000</link><description>以色列总理猛烈抨击军队和安全部门的决定进一步加剧了对他在利库德集团内部领导的批评</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 04:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tweet-could-hasten-his-ouster-party-colleagues-say/0000018b-7c8b-d51e-a3cb-7def36cb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布三名人质视频，要求内塔尼亚胡同意交换人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article-live/idf-attacks-in-syria-following-rocket-launches-antisemitic-riots-in-russian-airport/0000018b-7df0-d4a8-a3cf-fdf9c8530000</link><description>以色列军队正在扩大对加沙的地面入侵，以色列国防军称在 24 小时内袭击了 600 个恐怖目标 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部报告称，超过 8,000 名巴勒斯坦人被以色列军队杀害 ■ 以色列警察在耶路撒冷发生刺伤袭击，身受重伤 ■ 四人巴勒斯坦人在以色列国防军袭击约旦河西岸杰宁时丧生 ■ 以色列空军连夜袭击了叙利亚和黎巴嫩的目标 ■ 哈马斯扣押的人质人数为 239 人，仍有 40 名人失踪 ■ 10 月 7 日，哈马斯大屠杀至少造成 1,300 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 03:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article-live/idf-attacks-in-syria-following-rocket-launches-antisemitic-riots-in-russian-airport/0000018b-7df0-d4a8-a3cf-fdf9c8530000</guid></item><item><title>康奈尔希勒尔建议犹太学生和工作人员因受到威胁而避免去犹太餐厅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/cornell-hillel-asks-jewish-students-and-staff-to-avoid-kosher-dining-hall-due-to-threats/0000018b-7e47-d4a8-a3cf-feef43990000</link><description>校园里的犹太学生表示，在一个与学校没有正式关系的讨论板上发布了呼吁杀害和强奸犹太人的令人不安的帖子后，他们不敢离开宿舍。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 02:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/cornell-hillel-asks-jewish-students-and-staff-to-avoid-kosher-dining-hall-due-to-threats/0000018b-7e47-d4a8-a3cf-feef43990000</guid></item><item><title>以色列会吸取费卢杰的教训吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/will-israel-learn-the-lessons-of-fallujah/0000018b-7cf0-d4a8-a3cf-fcf9bf710000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 22:29:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/will-israel-learn-the-lessons-of-fallujah/0000018b-7cf0-d4a8-a3cf-fcf9bf710000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的联盟必须立即罢免他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/edit